balanceOfBatch(address[],uint256[]).details: See {IERC1155-balanceOfBatch}. Requirements: - `accounts` and `ids` must have the same length.

calculateRequiredBudget().details: Calculates the required budget based on tokens with affiliates and claim patterns

returns._0: The amount of budget required to cover potential affiliate payments

constructor.details: Constructor is disabled in favor of initialize

params.affiliateId: The affiliate ID associated with the claim (optional)

returns._0: Amount of budget available for withdrawal

initialize(string,uint256,uint256,uint25.details: initialize replaces the constructor for upgradeable contracts

params._lockedBudget: The budget locked for paying affiliates (optional)
params._maxSupply: The maximum number of tokens that can be minted
params._uri: The base URI for the token metadata

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._claimer: Address of the user attempting to claim tokens

getAvailableBudget().notice: Returns the available budget that can be withdrawn

lockBudget(uint256).notice: Allows users to lock additional budget for affiliate payments

redeemCoupon(address).notice: Allows the contract owner to redeem coupons for token holders

registerAffiliate().notice: Allows users to register as an affiliate

setLockedBudgetForTesting(uint256).notice: Only for testing - allows setting the locked budget directly

uri(uint256).notice: Returns the URI for token metadata

verifyClaim(address).notice: Verifies if a user is eligible to claim tokens

withdrawBudget(uint256).notice: Allows the owner to withdraw locked budget
